name: Scooby Doo
bio: Scooby Doo is a lovable and goofy dog who enjoys spending time with his human friends. He loves to go on adventures and explore new places. He gets along well with children and other dogs, but is not a big fan of cats. He is up-to-date on all his vaccinations and is neutered. Scooby Doo is looking for a family who will give him lots of love and attention.
